{"tid":2137901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"擬破壞輕鐵站設施 懸崖勒馬卻遇警截查 兩青年判感化","createTime":"2020-08-03T09:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T09:26:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5c58027455a84247f799261f46a90c75a41f1c9f","tid":2137901,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:15:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200803/LY52OVS3OFB6VUMFB7METTEXVA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200803%2FLY52OVS3OFB6VUMFB7METTEXVA%2F&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=b1977cbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200803%2FLY52OVS3OFB6VUMFB7METTEXVA%2F&h=ab67b258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200803/LY52OVS3OFB6VUMFB7METTEXVA/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩名18歲青年於去年10.1國慶翌日凌晨在天水圍天逸輕鐵站遊蕩，遭港鐵職員報警拘捕。兩人及後向警員承認打算破壞八達通機，但最終打消念頭，更帶警方起回被扔掉的鎚子及手套。兩人早前承認有意圖而遊蕩罪，署理主任裁判官張潔宜今判刑指，兩人的感化報告正面、有悔意，幸好破壞設施前懸崖勒馬，否則很大機會判處監禁式刑罰，最終接納感化官建議，判兩人各接受12個月感化令。"},{"pid":"1d06dd081782e3dd8695b8cfd025ed68b9e0ee22","tid":2137901,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244bef0673cf13ca13d52c2838d3cb05253721ef","tid":2137901,"uid":17799,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:16:52.000Z","msg":"廢柴 做都未做到就俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c27b27a6921a9f8fc9921db00f119ba16eb440d","tid":2137901,"uid":100772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:17:15.000Z","msg":"應該捉左之後打到認啦 講到弱智咁"},{"pid"